      Get Tickets
    </legend>
    <p>
      The event is FREE to attend and all ages are welcome. GET YOUR FREE TICKETS AT EVENTBRITE.COM To participate in
      each station you will need 1 ticket or 1 "SMASH cash". Each ticket is $1, but don't let money put a stop to a
      great time, you can also earn "SMASH cash" when you learn about composting and other ways to live more sustainably
      while having fun! Here is how: Walk around the event and read the posters with information about composting and
      recycling, then visit the "SMASH cash station" and answer some questions, if you get them right, you will earn
      "SMASH cash" and can spend it having more fun!
    </p>
  </fieldset>
</div>
